      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for primary QoI.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic material model with frictional contact at screw-rod interface. Model form selection justified by absence of plastic deformation in F1717 stiffness regime; contact formulation validated against published analytical solutions."
