      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Material properties (Ti-6Al-4V: E=114 GPa, ν=0.34) sourced from ASTM F136 and confirmed by coupon tensile testing. Geometric dimensions derived from CMM measurements of physical constructs used in validation experiments."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
