      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "FEA boundary conditions replicate the F1717 test fixture geometry and loading axis. Load application point, constraint locations, and fixture stiffness all mapped from physical fixture CAD drawings and confirmed by back-calculation from experimental load-displacement data."
