      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison using area validation metric (AVM) per ASME V&V 20. FEA construct stiffness predictions fell within ±8% of experimental mean across all 11 specimens. AVM score of 0.92 exceeds acceptance threshold of 0.80."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
