    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficient factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted under a documented risk-benefit determination: the F1717 protocol specifies a single canonical test condition, and no alternative multi-condition dataset exists for this construct geometry. Overall credibility is judged sufficient for the intended regulatory submission.",
